<p>WebSocket是一种在单个<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/TCP" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">TCP</a>连接上进行<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%85%A8%E5%8F%8C%E5%B7%A5" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">全双工</a>通信的协议。</p>
